        public boolean canAdd(dfischer.webadmininterface.DisplayListCache displayListCache,
             long startId,
             long endId,
             ProxySnifferTransactionHandler proxySnifferTransactionHandler)
        Check if a URL loop can be added. A new URL loop cannot be added if it overlaps another URL loop.
        Parameters:
        displayListCache - displayListCache
        startId - data record ID of URL loop start
        endId - data record ID of URl loop end
        Returns:
        true if the URL loop can be added, or false if the URL loop cannot be added
